lt=\"\">\n                </picture>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"swiper-slide fv_swiper_slide\">\n                <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/fv_img3.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/fv_img3.jpg\">\n                    <source srcset=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/fv_img3_sp.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n                    <img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/fv_img3_sp.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                </picture>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"swiper-pagination swiper_common_pagination fv_swiper_pagination\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"fv_contents\">\n        <div class=\"fv_logo\">\n            <picture>\n                <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/fv_logo.svg\">\n                <img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/fv_logo_sp.svg\" alt=\"Trust creates energy\">\n            </picture>\n            <p class=\"fv_lead\">\n                <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/fv_text.svg\">\n                    <img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/fv_text_sp.svg\" alt=\"信頼が、エネルギーをつくる。 \">\n                </picture>\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"t-about\" id=\"about\">\n    <div class=\"inner\">\n        <hgroup class=\"section_ttl\">\n            <p><img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/ttl_about.svg\" alt=\"About us\"></p>\n            <h2>サンベ電気とは</h2>\n        </hgroup>\n        <div class=\"t-about_wrap\">\n            <div class=\"t-about_img\"><img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/about_img.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></div>\n            <div class=\"t-about_contents\">\n                <p class=\"t-about_lead\">サンベ電気は、<br class=\"is_pc\">お客さまとの<br class=\"is_sp\">信頼関係を<br class=\"is_pc\">大切にしています。</p>\n                <p class=\"t-about_text\">サンベ電気は、「社員ファースト」の考えをもとに、長く働き続ける職場にしていくことはじめ、社員やその家族が安心して暮らしていけるよう、生活へのバックアップも重視しています。その中でも特に充実しているのが「福利厚生」です。</p>\n                <a href=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/about-us\" class=\"button_more\"><span class=\"more\">MORE</span></a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"t-works bg_green\" id=\"works\">\n    <div class=\"inner\">\n        <hgroup class=\"section_ttl\">\n            <p><img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/ttl_works.svg\" alt=\"Works\"></p>\n            <h2>業務案内</h2>\n        </hgroup>\n        <ul class=\"t-works_lists\">\n            <li class=\"t-works_list\">\n                <div class=\"t-works_texts\">\n                    <p class=\"t-works_lead\">サンベ電気は<br>設計・積算・図面・見積・照明、<br>エアコン等の仕入れから工事まで<br>一式すべて対応可能です！</p>\n                    <p class=\"t-works_text\">電気関係の工事事業なら何でも対応いたしております。お気軽にご相談ください。また、環境に優しい ECO電力の太陽光発電は高くなる一方の電気代、光熱費を安く抑えたい方に必見です。</p>\n                </div>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"t-works_list\">\n                <a href=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/ordinary-household\" class=\"t-works_link\">\n                    <div class=\"t-works_head\">\n                        <h3 class=\"t-works_head_title\"><span class=\"num\"><img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/works_01.svg\" alt=\"01\"></span>一般家庭向け<br>電気工事</h3>\n                        <p class=\"t-works_head_more\">MORE</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"t-works_list_img\">\n                        <div class=\"img\">\n                            <img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/works_img1.png\" alt=\"image\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"t-works_list_en\">Ordinary household</div>\n                    </div>\n                </a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"t-works_list\">\n                <a href=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/store-building-renovation\" class=\"t-works_link\">\n                    <div class=\"t-works_head\">\n                        <h3 class=\"t-works_head_title\"><span class=\"num\"><img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/works_02.svg\" alt=\"02\"></span>店舗ビル改修・<br>リフォーム工事</h3>\n                        <p class=\"t-works_head_more\">MORE</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"t-works_list_img\">\n                        <div class=\"img\">\n                            <picture>\n                                <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/works_img2.png\">\n                                <img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/works_img2_sp.png\" alt=\"image\">\n                            </picture>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"t-works_list_en\">Store building / Renovation</div>\n                    </div>\n                </a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"t-works_list\">\n                <a href=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/large-electrical-equipment\" class=\"t-works_link\">\n                    <div class=\"t-works_head\">\n                        <h3 class=\"t-works_head_title\"><span class=\"num\"><img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/works_03.svg\" alt=\"03\"></span>公共・大型<br>電気設備工事</h3>\n                        <p class=\"t-works_head_more\">MORE</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"t-works_list_img\">\n                        <div class=\"img\">\n                            <img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/works_img3.png\" alt=\"image\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"t-works_list_en\">Large Electrical Equipment</div>\n                    </div>\n                </a>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n        <a href=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/solar-power-generation\" class=\"t-works_solar\">\n            <div class=\"t-works_solar_img\">\n                <div class=\"img\">\n                    <img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/works_solar.png\" alt=\"image\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"t-works_solar_wrap\">\n                <div class=\"t-works_solar_contents\">\n                    <hgroup class=\"t-works_solar_title\">\n                        <h3>太陽光発電ECO電力</h3>\n                        <p>Solar power generation</p>\n                    </hgroup>\n                    <p class=\"t-works_solar_text\">太陽光発電は環境に配慮しながら光熱費を節約できます。さらに、オール電化を組み合わせれば、さらに有効に使え、大幅な光熱費の削減が期待できます。</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </a>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<div class=\"bg_black\">\n        <section class=\"t-news\">\n        <div class=\"inner inner_s t_news_wrap\">\n            <div class=\"t_news_head\">\n                <hgroup class=\"section_ttl text_white\">\n                    <p><img src=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/wp-content/themes/sanbedenki/img/top/ttl_news.svg\" alt=\"News\"></p>\n                    <h2>新着ニュース</h2>\n                </hgroup>\n                <a href=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/archives/news\" class=\"t_news_archive\">一覧を見る</a>\n            </div>\n            <ul class=\"news_lists t_news_lists\">\n                                <li class=\"news_list\">\n                    <a href=\"https://sanbe-denki.co.jp/archives/news/%e3%8